 {"file_name": "Landscape Portrait.png", "id": "840716281119571", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_PORTRAIT", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/57574720_840716291119570_6338633741422904364_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=LRHJqaIhjcEQ7kNvgHCLQU8&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAaZunEE3uejMsKtbl6Kl133WgD4yDBPkjt8FKsElFfzA&oe=66FFBD5B"}, {"file_name": "Icon.png", "id": "488412717275961", "image_type": "APP_IMG_ICON", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974525_488412720609294_7458364120634917665_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=xxOSi1uuyk0Q7kNvgGUXeCj&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYA7wvQQHv-lBQY6Gu9-N8LLdfyXvjVzKgLP4S8sh5Qqhw&oe=66FFE6D1"}, {"file_name": "Landscape Square.png", "id": "427144199756021", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_SQUARE", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75223486_427144203089354_4369279694658394896_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=YCsguHoj4v0Q7kNvgE99-gL&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDyNwpvs0zYpXfqIT6ZFExPEohFoUFMT4muUWA9tvBnxg&oe=66FFC58F"}]}, "id": "1062082695522073", "locale": "it_IT", "screenshots": [{"file_name": "Artboard 5.png", "id": "422140790868918", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031547_422140794202251_1640211663921085746_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=qLThEBUEebAQ7kNvgHOdbTi&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYB4GEim_bdDzWZ49j4BFmSQEVQuoNNrokhAooye90wifA&oe=66FFCDAA"}, {"file_name": "Artboard 2.png", "id": "468838062692515", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38984464_468838066025848_9209980070403449565_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=N9sKF7Yr2xcQ7kNvgGPgwYK&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCzRbG71YDIw-fhYqlYgi2COR2_mmr7Pxco7Y9sSJCVYg&oe=66FFC98C"}, {"file_name": "Artboard 4.png", "id": "481654227990009", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031353_481654234656675_3114596455803752280_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=TBB76Zm-1kQQ7kNvgGt4xoa&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBC9I6xH4L1pntehDlu3A3k9uXlugnKAaomWu-hoqmmKA&oe=66FFC810"}, {"file_name": "Artboard 3.png", "id": "3889565187981667", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031547_3889565191315000_5528783709779854295_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=wvhkhkFP8zwQ7kNvgGSplcr&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYC0Y40w6-P6nesrLKxxUbHpTgSvGhiSbOv69pPUnFWlwQ&oe=66FFC7A4"}, {"file_name": "Artboard 1.png", "id": "867384681933118", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39003244_867384685266451_2340853765823917163_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=mpOFdtrwTdkQ7kNvgHKlyW8&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBVObNSkP68ylONSsl1m8guY1XexeaP5lhyR2HYrzyOjg&oe=66FFCBC5"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "38974450_2251639131854765_8396477208328520911_n.png", "id": "999991165259980", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75476756_999991168593313_5483195490028886346_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=Arl-bTTq9VAQ7kNvgG-I51T&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAElKYHQ3bFwow9zZYPQH7m4K_1llyQnwDsmafUBAdIfA&oe=66FFD931"}, "display_name": "Safari Cellulare", "keywords": [], "long_description": "**Safari Cellulare** \u00e8 un'applicazione di realt\u00e0 virtuale innovativa che trasforma l'apprendimento della **biologia cellulare** in un'avventura emozionante. Progettata per **studenti, educatori e appassionati di scienza**, questa app ti permette di esplorare una **cellula animale in 3D** come mai prima d'ora. Attraverso un'interfaccia immersiva, puoi navigare tra le diverse strutture cellulari, come **il nucleo, i mitocondri e il reticolo endoplasmatico**, scoprendone le funzioni e l'importanza.\n\nOgni componente della cellula \u00e8 rappresentato con dettagli straordinari, permettendoti di osservare e comprendere i processi biologici complessi in modo visivamente accattivante. **L'intelligenza artificiale integrata** \u00e8 a tua disposizione per rispondere a qualsiasi domanda tu possa avere durante l'esplorazione, fornendo spiegazioni chiare e dettagliate.\n\nSafari Cellulare non \u00e8 solo un'esperienza educativa passiva; include una serie di **mini giochi interattivi** progettati per consolidare le tue conoscenze in modo divertente e coinvolgente. Attraverso **sfide e quiz**, puoi mettere alla prova la tua comprensione dei concetti biologici, rendendo l'apprendimento un processo attivo e stimolante.\n\nPerfetta per l'uso in ambito educativo o come strumento di autoapprendimento, Safari Cellulare offre un modo nuovo e innovativo per esplorare il mondo microscopico della cellula animale. Con **grafica di alta qualit\u00e0** e un'**esperienza utente intuitiva**, questa app trasforma lo studio della biologia in un'avventura indimenticabile.", "short_description": "Scopri l'affascinante mondo della cellula animale con Safari Cellulare, l'app VR educativa che ti permette di esplorare le strutture cellulari in 3D. Attraverso mini giochi interattivi e un'intelligenza artificiale avanzata, apprendi concetti scientifici divertendoti. Ideale per studenti e appassionati di biologia, questa esperienza immersiva rende l'apprendimento un'avventura entusiasmante."}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "Logo.png", "id": "7830788620364802", "image_type": "APP_IMG_LOGO_TRANSPARENT", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974477_7830788637031467_2492816240902607915_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=5yqtNtJgM2wQ7kNvgGAxkim&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCfBy4aTdEkJ44_qOdqxhY-zgEEPidRTKxCijqY7t3oyA&oe=66FFDEAC"}, {"file_name": "Landscape Portrait.png", "id": "1994643360958356", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_PORTRAIT", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75462955_1994643364291689_8067620305322327621_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=t6YisyCXHUsQ7kNvgFFwio3&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAYRRa7QfrW3gDttI1dTPIm5FY5AZjVNiZ3IhEQiY9wig&oe=66FFC40F"}, {"file_name": "Icon.png", "id": "1749848195756080", "image_type": "APP_IMG_ICON", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39003273_1749848199089413_6210488408238311147_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=O6PENtG5O8QQ7kNvgFmz9-R&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDQ5CSTEjX70oJ2Pi7XMA6ME7o4xznjZztRF2R8mfkq7w&oe=66FFC006"}, {"file_name": "Hero Cover.png", "id": "1019117086331658", "image_type": "APP_IMG_HERO", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974548_1019117092998324_1164601898764144918_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=_XkiqnvQ-fYQ7kNvgGvtoGs&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCH4AwGgHboAwuKQhrVdZWqiurt0kKPCE14eKxWKPaRaw&oe=66FFDA28"}, {"file_name": "Landscape.png", "id": "872400761490753", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031450_872400768157419_814239069343010651_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=UIVUkAlw7M8Q7kNvgFGZ-VH&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYB-eM4HeICfc24q5Ru14BmREBQZYG2kvf6hQXjcciGZ5g&oe=66FFBE23"}, {"file_name": "Landscape Mini.png", "id": "513806047726163", "image_type": "APP_IMG_SMALL_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982645_513806051059496_4223857969464332917_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=3q8lo5tP6PkQ7kNvgEeeIZy&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDMlbeH5PrbGIZTHsaPVD97JXaVu_YgYAjaSd5nSdRvGg&oe=66FFD38B"}, {"file_name": "Landscape Square.png", "id": "493094060118611", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_SQUARE", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031398_493094063451944_436248626179243058_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=-XCs1snSxTwQ7kNvgH63R4K&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAS7R-k6xrf8laAaadEdrWLjx7qtLznTQ544SvGsihmIw&oe=66FFD819"}]}, "id": "1030659978605601", "locale": "en_US", "screenshots": [{"file_name": "Artboard 5.png", "id": "2759662717526847", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39036623_2759662720860180_2489395151907338724_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=LZS3uHSb9A0Q7kNvgE-NTPw&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBxuUMyb7gU2RuiFiR8im0EyiZoxFOYu1o0OU1wJoLIqQ&oe=66FFE9F2"}, {"file_name": "Artboard 4.png", "id": "2251639125188099", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974450_2251639131854765_8396477208328520911_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=cALAW44M8fAQ7kNvgEoVLLm&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBhxeMF9YVqlyAxw-VVDXFL2ZWjR9ISFo4jG4UYdoi2Rw&oe=66FFD729"}, {"file_name": "Artboard 2.png", "id": "473243412277688", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38984439_473243418944354_2938823070153890993_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=ghhWhwtEVwsQ7kNvgHCsgaA&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDY496wY-sBjQB0MluEShNmwYSR6eCXoey6lqYIhbxXvA&oe=66FFBFB7"}, {"file_name": "Artboard 1.png", "id": "1543351499921825", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974887_1543351503255158_348442130487521407_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=OaLUgTMDcYoQ7kNvgG-uwiW&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDBVL1P42jMJJS8nGLH3Gi-xUyz_EDhF79lGWAT3DbHmg&oe=66FFC5C6"}, {"file_name": "Artboard 3.png", "id": "912383657378781", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031432_912383660712114_2572436446715478623_n.png?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=3_7xQnQXFmEQ7kNvgFgwmqD&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYB85umBrzWnRwKVeDvI9yNHuc6uQMrYxemFzoK4jnEdwg&oe=66FFE4FA"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "38974450_2251639131854765_8396477208328520911_n.png", "id": "3748813912049179", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031311_3748813915382512_2166423531006939259_n.png?_nc_cat=110&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=uBTMpdjo4L0Q7kNvgGU3aOS&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYATyQGx7-LBTjDfJPMXkwqkiNA7J5px7ZWreerfGOzPyg&oe=66FFC14D"}, "display_name": "Cellular Safari", "keywords": [], "long_description": "**Safari Cellular** is an innovative virtual reality app that turns learning about **cellular biology** into an exciting adventure. Designed for **students, educators and science enthusiasts**, this app allows you to explore an **animal cell in 3D** like never before. Through an immersive interface, you can navigate through different cell structures, such as **the nucleus, mitochondria, and endoplasmic reticulum**, discovering their functions and importance.\n\nEach component of the cell is represented in stunning detail, allowing you to observe and understand complex biological processes in a visually engaging way. **Integrated artificial intelligence** is at your disposal to answer any questions you may have while exploring, providing clear and detailed explanations.\n\nCellular Safari is not just a passive educational experience; it includes a series of **mini interactive games** designed to consolidate your knowledge in a fun and engaging way. Through **challenges and quizzes**, you can test your understanding of biological concepts, making learning an active and stimulating process.\n\nPerfect for use in education or as a self-study tool, Cellular Safari offers a new and innovative way to explore the microscopic world of the animal cell. With **high-quality graphics** and an **intuitive user experience**, this app turns the study of biology into an unforgettable adventure.", "short_description": "Discover the fascinating world of the animal cell with Cell Safari, the educational VR app that lets you explore cellular structures in 3D. Through interactive mini-games and advanced artificial intelligence, learn scientific concepts while having fun. Ideal for students and biology enthusiasts, this immersive experience makes learning an exciting adventure."}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "Landscape Mini.png", "id": "7934545376658361", "image_type": "APP_IMG_SMALL_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.